to her as Cesar's sidekick or,

01:25:37.465 --> 01:25:40.366
in the case of Home,
actually saying his girlfriend,

01:25:40.435 --> 01:25:42.836
it was a perfect example
why we need ethnic studies

01:25:42.904 --> 01:25:46.534
because we have people in power
at the policy level

01:25:46.608 --> 01:25:49.805
that have no idea of
the true heroes of this country.

01:25:49.878 --> 01:25:52.370
