ourselves and what do they say?

01:27:48.329 --> 01:27:50.140
As a woman, you're just thinking
about yourself,

01:27:50.164 --> 01:27:51.859
then you are what?
Selfish, right?

01:27:51.933 --> 01:27:55.892
If a woman is assertive,
they use the B word, right?

01:27:55.970 --> 01:27:58.940
